 Avoid breathing gas. Store and use with adequate ventilation.  Keep oil, grease, and combustibles away.  Use only use with equipment cleaned as for oxygen service and rated for cylinder pressure.  Do not get liquid in eyes, or on skin, or in clothing.  Cylinder temperature should not exceed 125’F (52’C). Open valve slowly. Close valve after each use.  Keep closed even when empty.  Always secure cylinder.  Install cap If provided, when not in use. Use backflow prevention device in any piping. Use per Praxair MSDS form P-4636. Praxair safety booklet P-14-153. And manufacturer’s operating instructions for this container.  Obtain Praxair publications from your local supplier.

Rx ONLY

